<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.1">
<l>taṉṉai naivik kileṉval viṉaiyēṉ toḻutumeḻu</l>
<l>poṉṉai naivikku mappūñ cerunti maṇanīḻalvāy</l>
<l>eṉṉai naivitte ḻilkoṇ ṭakaṉṟa perumāṉiṭam</l>
<l>puṉṉai muttam poḻilcūḻn taḻakā yapullāṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I of harsh fate ruin myself, what [then]? Arise; we will worship</l>
<l>In beautiful Pullāṇi with garden tracts of laurel encircling,</l>
<l>The place of the lord who, draining my complexion, left, having ruined me</l>
<l>In the fragrant shade of a pear tree with fine blooming flowers</l>
<l rend="indent">which ruin [the beauty of] gold.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
